graph TD
    A[Start] --> B[Create Feature Branch<br>from main]
    B --> C[Run Claim Slot Workflow]
    C --> D[Workflow creates PR<br>to update slot-assignment.yml]
    D --> E{PR Merged?}
    E -- Yes --> F[Slot Assigned!]
    E -- No --> D
    
    subgraph SLOT [Isolated Development in a Slot]
        F --> G[Develop & Push Code<br>to Feature Branch]
        G --> H(CI/CD Pipeline Triggered)
        H --> I[Builds Container Image<br>Deploys to Isolated DEV]
        I --> J[Tests run using<br>dedicated Dataset & DAGs]
        J --> K{Ready for<br>Isolated UAT?}
        K -- No --> G
        K -- Yes --> L[Trigger Deploy to<br>Isolated UAT Workflow]
        L --> M[Promotes build to<br>Isolated UAT]
        M --> N{UAT Testing<br>Passed?}
        N -- No --> G
    end
    
    N -- Yes --> O[Merge Feature Branch<br>to shared dev branch]
    
    subgraph RELEASE [Standard Integration & Release]
        O --> P[Run Release Slot Workflow]
        P --> Q[Standard Promotion Pipeline<br>dev to uat to prd]
    end
    
    Q --> R[End]
    
    style A fill:#90EE90
    style R fill:#FF9999
    style F fill:#87CEEB
    style O fill:#FFD700
